description:
Though Coco Pommel is sweet and talented, she struggles when it comes to all things romance. With the help of Princess Cadence and Shining Armor will she finally be win the heart of a certain special somepony before Hearts & Hooves day is over? Find how now!
If you like my work please consider supporting me on twitter and on patreon
Twitter: https://x.com/TheTamers12345
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/c/Tamers12345
